Gmail Cleaner Pro UI - COMPLETED

✅ Complete implementation with all PRD features:

## Features Implemented:

### 1. Dashboard Tab
- Stats cards showing weekly/monthly cleaned emails
- Last cleanup timestamp
- Recent activity log with scrollable history (localStorage)
- Quick action buttons (Start Chat, Run Cleanup Now)
- Gmail connection status indicator

### 2. Chat Interface Tab
- Real-time chat with Ad-hoc Cleaner Agent (69787126a75ef8a94cc4f0d1)
- Message bubbles with timestamps
- Email preview panel with selectable cards
- Email cards with sender avatar, name, subject, date, category tag
- Action bar: Select All, Delete Selected (red button)
- Text input with send button
- Suggestion chips for common requests
- Inline error handling (no toast/sonner)

### 3. Settings Tab
- Email type toggles (Promotional, Old emails)
- Age threshold dropdown (7/14/30/60/90 days)
- Schedule section (frequency, time picker)
- Safety settings (confirmation toggle, max emails limit)
- Save Settings and Test Run buttons
- Periodic Cleaner Agent integration (697871441b6268d7b95195f6)

## Technical Implementation:

✅ TypeScript interfaces based on ACTUAL test response schemas
✅ Used callAIAgent from @/utils/aiAgent for all agent interactions
✅ Real agent IDs hardcoded from workflow.json
✅ Activity history persisted in localStorage
✅ Settings persisted in localStorage
✅ Inline status messages (no toast/sonner)
✅ Professional blue/white theme with red accent for delete actions
✅ All lucide-react icons (NO react-icons)
✅ Responsive layout with proper error handling
✅ Loading states with spinners
✅ Single-page app with tab navigation

## Response Integration:

Ad-hoc Agent Response Fields:
- action, emails_found, emails_deleted
- criteria_identified (sender, date_range, category, keywords)
- email_preview[] array
- confirmation_required, message

Periodic Agent Response Fields:
- cleanup_summary (total_emails_processed, total_emails_deleted, rules_executed, execution_time_seconds)
- rules_results[] array
- next_scheduled_run, errors[]

All fields properly mapped to UI components!

## File Structure:
- src/pages/Home.tsx (1029 lines - complete implementation)
- All components defined inline (DashboardStats, ActivityLogList, EmailPreviewCard)
- NO separate component files created
- NO API routes created (uses callAIAgent utility)

Build ready for deployment!
